data.description: This is a beautiful home sitting on a hill with Lake Martin Views .  You can fish and enjoy the serenity of the small town quietness ! Or if you like to entertain this is the home ! Primary Bedroom has a fireplace ,Double  Closets &   all the amenities of Double Vanity, Walk in shower and large soaking tub. The other four bedrooms have 2 bath    tubs and showers. Plus 2 studies or media rooms to fit your lifestyle. Plus a basement for your safety !  Come take a look and fall in love with this wonderful home!
